Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼對他開口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不怪你 這是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,錯的是戰爭?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不能這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣無法拯救里希特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們繼續300年前的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就在這裡 現在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,為了犒勞各位長時間在過去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,暢喝 暢吃 暢玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,暢玩?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我請客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1055,985)}pa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,盡興吧 盡興
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,來啊 各位怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼不起勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 喝啊喝啊  - No No
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 這就不行了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你也弱了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 120°的酒?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,難怪不行了 誒嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒在喝啊 來嘛來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 四眼 不喝嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 把眼鏡還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 況且我憑什麼要做這麼無聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,等我300年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,300年後 等我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就陪你玩到盡興
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,倒酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是老樣子 餓虎吞食一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 園原呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她說她在遠處看著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你們幾個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不許剩 都喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我就暢玩囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 她逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,喝啊 喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我確實逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 再下去要被灌死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,或者說會被亂摸一氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽菜 我們也逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽菜?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我們繼續300年前的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就在這裡 現在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,色色色蘿莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,蘿莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,蘿莉色色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼行 怎麼能對小孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就是個小孩吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我是小孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我和里希特先生沒差幾歲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不 差多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我是活了300多年的老爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事等你長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,和你真正喜歡的人做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 當我是小孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 痛痛痛…小陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我的小嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽菜 你要幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喝啊 喝啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 小陽菜?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,玩她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我很樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,暢玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,年輕的胸 不受重力影響的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,教教我 奈奈姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,內衣我…我不知道怎麼弄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你冷靜 里希特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,鈎子在前面 還是後面?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,鈎子? 什麼鈎子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果玩了琳小姐的胸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那也玩我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,況且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,事到如今 怎麼了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,明明之前好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,想偷看我裙底
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你這軟蛋 渣男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不玩我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嫌我的小嗎? 嫌我小嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是因為 珍惜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有一點我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙 和我在一起300年都沒摘下面具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我的沒法滿足你嗎… - 遇見陽菜以後 突然就摘下來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 是陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看見我 里希特會想起那場戰爭的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好 開喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你和300年前 一模一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你有時候 太隱忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭 才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是喝醉了就愛哭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這點就醉了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是酒 酒進眼裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你 對這麼個阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼溫柔 有意思嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你 別看我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,現在是暢玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,來啊 來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼突然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,佩雷 把那個借給他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是借來的那個對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 這樣可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,噔噔噔 戰爭終於結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我作為軍人的工作結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,今後我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,想成為哥哥的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,50年後 里希特一直都沒摘下面具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,100年後 一句話都不說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,今天發生了件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然只有一點 里希特開口說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,然後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,等里希特摘下面具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我想告訴他 要當他的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然成了這樣的阿姨 也行吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟我等了200年了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你們 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,每每看到我 里希特都會想起那場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,求你們 救救他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只靠我 已經救不了我最喜歡的哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 里希特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我當時 還只是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦 所以…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:10:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不是因為每每看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,都會想起那場戰爭 才不摘面具的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是 不知道該作何表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想讓你擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,連假笑都笑不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因為有你一直陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我才能活過這300年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己一個人會瘋的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我該早點告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想當新娘 能給我答覆嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 我還是被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,其實 因為我當時也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我也花心了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我會一直陪著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 睡過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,今天沒關係嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不踏出第一步 就無從改變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}軟蛋 渣男
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,咦? 大家人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,年輕真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不像年過300的阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,300歲比起阿姨 應該叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 天氣真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好 今天要喝個夠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是「也要」吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好 里希特 趕緊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我上個廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎? 快回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好 開喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,咦? 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,年份上好的酒啊 這我沒買過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上布丁小哥說 回過神來就在懷裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,犯法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 就當不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 喝吧喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,來 你也喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 有罪犯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我作為軍人…  - 夠了閉嘴喝酒 正經四眼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很好很好 酒會開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不能這麼喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,沒下酒菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,沒就做一個唄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 平時做菜接客那是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,開始喝了就不想工作啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,話說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,借我一下廚房的話 我可以做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小琳太棒啦 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也 去把動物…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,陽菜就算啦 喝吧喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,夠爽快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:15:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,來 再來一瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,掛芡豆腐 涼拌豆芽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,涼拌酸甜黃瓜雞胸肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,還比不上專業的奈奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,小琳 將來會是個好媳婦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 明明菜的熱量這麼低
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,盯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要是肚子上沒肉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是肥…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,停 再說就是性騷擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,況且女生衣服脫了都會有肉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,奈奈小姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為這個才不穿泳裝的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,想看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了? 四眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,內衣和泳裝沒什麼區別吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 我自己想脫就脫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說我太隱忍了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,內衣的鈎子你了解嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不 只是奈奈小姐比較奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細看的話 小陽菜肚子上也一定有肉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,坐著也沒肚子 真有這種人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 這也太細了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,臉和身材都很嬌小 可前凸後翹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是洋娃娃嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,洋娃娃什麼時候會走路說話喝酒了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 喂 肥…  - 住口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒完 反正她一定在看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,園原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,現在立刻換上泳裝吧 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,女生一般脫了肚子上都有肉的吧 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你回來啦 肥…  - 性騷擾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 光是跑兩步可瘦不下來哦 肥…  - 性騷擾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該多跑點 減下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,性騷擾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,性騷擾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:18:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽菜?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,開搞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,來人吶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這隻蘿莉 有毛病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,救命 住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,來人吶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生 總是拋下人家不管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次見面的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,說好要一起吃飯的 還拋下了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,裴爾默那次也是 本以為總算找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,還想支開我逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,從300年前回來以後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這次又突然躲著我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你又會 離開我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你又會 拋下我 總有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你就這麼討厭我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嫌我是個小孩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是你媽媽叫你來找擊墜王的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事很重要 希望你認真回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽媽的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,月菜·法羅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:55.94,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,730)}「花心」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.63,0:22:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我終於能眼放激光了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,吃我的鋼鐵傑伊爾光線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,氣勢還不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,低吼吧 傑伊爾信念光線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:41.40,Next,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1643,840)}{\fad(200,0)}下集「雨」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,下集「雨」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這是雨水 不是淚水
