Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:17.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}彷彿一望無際
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:24.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}悲傷已煙消雲散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:31.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}為了不讓這份笑容黯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:39.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}我會一直在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:43.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}沒有淚水的明天過後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:47.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}會有溫柔的未來等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:54.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}即便是微弱的希望 也相信著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:58.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of life一定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:01.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Feel you heart 只屬於自己的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:06.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}迷茫的時候攜手前行
